---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About Us — Knowledge IAS Academy" description="A premier e-learning and in-centre coaching platform for UPSC aspirants, led by Mr. Ajay Sah.">
  <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-16 lg:pt-24 pb-8">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[45%] h-[70%] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,rgba(245,166,35,0.12),transparent_70%)] -z-10"></div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot"></span>About Us</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight">
        A <span class="gold-underline-animated">decade of mentorship</span> behind every aspirant.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)] max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Knowledge IAS Academy is a premier coaching platform for aspirants gearing up for the Civil Services Examination conducted by the Union Public Service Commission.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pb-20">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 prose-readable">
        <p>
          At the heart of our offerings lies our flagship programme — <strong>FOCUS SCHOOL</strong> — meticulously crafted to cater to the unique needs of school-going students with aspirations to embark on a career in the esteemed Civil Services.
        </p>
        <p>
          This specialised course serves as a stepping stone, providing a structured curriculum and comprehensive guidance to equip students with the necessary knowledge and skills from an early stage. Through a blend of interactive lectures, FOCUS SCHOOL ensures that students develop a strong foundation in the subjects essential for the UPSC exams, while also fostering critical thinking and analytical abilities crucial for success in the competitive arena of civil services.
        </p>
        <p>
          Knowledge IAS Academy operates under the expert supervision and leadership of <strong>Mr. Ajay Sah</strong>, who serves as both the Director and Founder of the academy. With an extensive background spanning over a decade in the realm of the Civil Services Examination, Mr. Sah brings a wealth of knowledge and experience to the forefront.
        </p>
        <p>
          Having taught a diverse range of subjects across numerous esteemed institutes throughout the country — including <em>GS Score, Next IAS, Chanakya IAS, Target UPSC</em> and <em>Quest IAS</em> — he has honed his expertise in guiding aspirants towards success in the UPSC exams.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mr. Sah's commitment to excellence is evident through his engagement in conducting seminars and webinars on Civil Services Exam-related topics in prestigious institutions such as the IITs, NITs, BHU, St. Stephen's, and Hindu College, among others.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <div class="card card-interactive p-6">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-semibold">Founder</p>
          <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-2xl">Mr. Ajay Sah</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Director &amp; Founder · Knowledge IAS Academy. 10+ years mentoring UPSC aspirants across India's leading institutes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-interactive p-6">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-semibold">Taught At</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
            <li>GS Score</li>
            <li>Next IAS</li>
            <li>Chanakya IAS</li>
            <li>Target UPSC</li>
            <li>Quest IAS</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-interactive p-6">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-semibold">Seminars &amp; Webinars</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
            <li>IITs &amp; NITs</li>
            <li>Banaras Hindu University</li>
            <li>St. Stephen's College</li>
            <li>Hindu College</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
